    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This sticky, adhesive fluid ignites when exposed to air.</p><p> As an action, you can throw this flask up to 20 feet, shattering it on impact.</p><p> Make a ranged attack against a creature or object, treating the alchemist's fire as an improvised weapon.</p><p> On a hit, the target takes 1d4 fire damage at the start of each of its turns.</p><p> A creature can end this damage by using its action to make a DC 10 Dexterity check to extinguish the flames.</p><p></p>",
